    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 20 min, remove the potatoes from the oven and crush them firmly with the base of a mug or a spatula</p><p>Sprinkle over <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Crowd the potatoes together for the best melty cheese!</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 7-8 min or until golden – these are your <strong>cheesy potatoes</strong></p>",
