    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Sicilian-style lamb meatballs</strong> with the <strong>cheesy potatoes</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> over the meatballs</p><p>Garnish with your<strong> salad </strong>and top with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
